        "class": "",
        "text": "), in kal, niph., and once only in hithp., occurs just eighty times, always in this sense, and almost always so rendered in the Authorized Version, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Let us",
